      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEUCE COUPE NZ (1) steps out for a new yard and brings some good form from Victoria. Was fourth last start at Bendigo and was a close second from this barrier at Bendigo last month. Can measure up. ALIVE AND FREE (5) produced another strong performance last time when he battled on bravely to finish second at this circuit and distance, beaten just over a metre. That made it back-to-back placings so the hoof is on the till. BUZZ BOMB (2) draws well and is on the radar having produced three decent efforts since winning at this venue. ROCKNROLL SPIRIT (3) cannot be left out after recording a sequence of three top-three finishes, the latest here three days ago when he missed by just a head.",
